 can be used for your ward events and activities.</p>
<p>You may schedule ward activities and events on any day of the week. Monday evenings from 7-9 p.m. are restricted to only ecclesiastical scheduling, but there is still a high demand for rooms that can accommodate more than 100 people on these nights. Please discuss alternate dates whenever possible.</p>
<p>Scheduling at BYU-Idaho can be as simple as 1-2-3</p>
<p>1. Become familiar with BYU-Idaho's&nbsp;<a href="x41327.xml" style="outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; cursor: pointer;">General</a><a href="x41327.xml"> Guidelines</a></p>
<p>2. Plan before you call by using the&nbsp;<a href="Documents/scheduling-office/Ward_Checklist.pdf">Ward Event Checklist</a></p>
<p>3. <a href="x41422.xml">Contact us</a></p>
